    <string name="privacy_body_1">The app reads sleep, steps, and heart rate from Health Connect only to build a short context message and send it to one Kin.</string>
    <string name="privacy_body_2">We do not use this data for ads or resale. In this version, data is processed locally on the phone, and only the final message sent to the Kindroid API leaves the device.</string>
